{
  "raw_html": "<button type='button' role='link' class='btn btn-link p-0 text-start' id='link_2' aria-label=\" M/s Armour Security (India) Ltd. versus Commissioner, CGST, Delhi East Commissionerate & Anr. pdf\"  class='noToken' href='#' onclick=javascript:open_pdf('2','2025','2025_8_1727_1788','2025INSC982'); ><font size='4'> <strong>M/S ARMOUR SECURITY (INDIA) LTD.<span class='fst-italic'> versus </span>COMMISSIONER, CGST, DELHI EAST COMMISSIONERATE & ANR. </strong>- <span class='escrText'>[2025] 8 S.C.R. 1727</span><span class='ncDisplay'>2025 INSC 982</span><input type='hidden' id='cnr' value=ESCR010007452025></button></font><br><strong>Coram : J.B. PARDIWALA<sup style=\"color: #268e97;font-size: 22px;top: 0;\" class=\"tooltip-sup\" data-tooltip=\"Author\">*</sup>, R MAHADEVAN</strong><br> Issue for Consideration The High Court dismissed the writ petition filed by the petitioner herein, and declined from interdicting the summons dated 16.01.2025 and 23.01.2025 respectively, issued to the petitioner u/s.70 of the Central Goods and Services Act) by the Commissioner, Central Good and Services Tax, Delhi East Commissionerate (respondent no.1). Headnotes&dagger; Central Goods and Service Tax Act, 2017 &ndash; s.6(2)(b) &ndash; Bar under: Held: Clause (b) of sub-section (2) of s.6 of the CGST Act and the equivalent State enactments<br><strong class='caseDetailsTD' ><span style='color:#212F3D' > Decision Date :</span><font color='green'> 14-08-2025</font><span style='color:#212F3D' > | Case No :</span><font color='green'> SPECIAL LEAVE PETITION (CIVIL) No. 6092/2025</font><span style='color:#212F3D' > | Disposal Nature :</span><font color='green'> Disposed off</font>   <span style='color:#212F3D' > |  Bench :</span><font color='green'> 2 Judges</font></strong><div class='row my-1 mt-2 border bg-light'><div class='col-auto'><a href='#' class='btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm my-1' onclick=open_splitview('2','2025','2025_8_1727_1788','2025INSC982','S')><i <i class='fas fa-columns me-2'></i>Split view</a></div><div class='col-auto'><a href='#' class='btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm my-1' onclick=open_splitview('2','2025','2025_8_1727_1788','2025INSC982','H'); ><i class='fas fa-file-alt me-2'></i>HTML view</a></div><div class='col-auto'><a href='#' class='btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm my-1' onclick=open_flip('2','2025','2025_8_1727_1788','2025INSC982');><i class='fas fa-book-open me-2' ></i>Flip view</a></div><div class='col-auto'><a href='#' class='btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm my-1' onclick=open_pdf('2','2025','2025_8_1727_1788','2025INSC982','N'); ><i class='fas fa-file-pdf me-2'></i>PDF</a></div></div>",
